This is the gkb, a GNOME pager applet to change your keymap with a mouse-click.
It's just a pre-code, so feel free to bomb me any suggestions, ideas.

Lot of thanx for Pablo Saratxaga <pablo@mandrakesoft.com>,
Carlos Lopez <natorro@themis.fciencias.unam.mx> for many beauty
pixmaps.

Thanks for Balazs Nagy <julian7@kva.hu> for his major help, and 
Charles Levert <charles@comm.polymtl.ca> for beautiful dynamic keyboard 
layout.


					Shooby Ban <bansz@szif.hu>
